product.title: 3,4 mm Green Standard Boundary Cable
product.short_description: The 3,4 mm green Robot mower boundary cable is a premium quality cable that works for ALL robot mower installations.
product.long_description: The 3,4 mm green Robot mower boundary cable is a premium quality cable that works for ALL robot mower installations. The cable is insulated with hard plastic to protect the wire. It is still very flexible and can be laid with all cable machines. The bigger robot mower boundary cable comes in high-quality wooden spools to prevent breakage on impact. All wires are meter-marked throughout. Fits any robotic lawn mowers. Available on drums of  5 / 25 / 50 / 100 / 150 / 250 / 500 / 800 meters with a diameter of 3,4 mm. Thickness on the Robot mower boundary cable 3,4 mm with more stable insulation than the original plastic. Cable roll size: 5/25/100/150/250/500/800 Meters – the 800 meters will fit all professional cable machines. Used for the installation of robot mowers, boundary loop, boundary cable, search cable, look-up loop, guide-wire and much more. For all Husqvarna Automower types such: 105 305 308 310 315 315X 320 330X 420 430X 440 450X 520 550 G2 G3 210C 220AC 230ACX 260ACX 265ACX SH Solar Hybrid For all Gardena types such as: R38Li R40Li R45Li R50Li R70Li R75Li R80Li R100Li R130Li R160Li R165 R180 Sileno Sileno+ Sileno City smart Sileno City smart Sileno smart Sileno+ For all McCulloch such as: ROB R600 and R1000 Bosch Indego 800 1000 1100 1200 connect WorX Landroid For all Robomow-autonomous models such as: MC300, MC500, MC1000, MC1200, MS-Serie, RL-series, RM-Series. For all Ambrogio types such as: L200-250 -Robot models For all Stihl/Viking iMow robots For all Hinda Miimo robots
